{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require all online businesses to have a 24/7 customer support helpline",
        "additional_details": "Many online businesses have no easy or immediate access to 24-hour phone lines in the event of theft, and many customers cannot contact online businesses in their most difficult times when they need immediate assistance. We believe that when you pay to use a platform or for a service, online businesses should provide fast contact in the event of theft or being hacked.",
        "background": "Require all online businesses to have a 24-hour customer support helpline that is staffed by humans and must be answered within 15 minutes.",
